# Purchase Request Flow (`purchase_request.html`)

Single-page wizard (4 steps) posting to **`/api/voucher`** (Vercel proxy → `TLCG_P2P_BACKEND.gs`). All actions route through the proxy — no direct GAS URL in the frontend.

---

## Backend coupling

- `getMasterData` → `TLCG_CORE_BACKEND` — employees, Goods-KTT, suppliers (shared with all workflows)
- `purchaseRequest` → `TLCG_P2P_BACKEND` — writes to `Purchase_Request_History` sheet; sends emails to requester + approvers
- `getPurchaseRequestHistory` → `TLCG_P2P_BACKEND` — returns `requests[]` with `items` (JSON) and `metadata` (JSON)
- `approvePurchaseRequest` → `TLCG_P2P_BACKEND` — updates `metadata.budgetStatus` / `metadata.supplierStatus`
- `rejectPurchaseRequest` → `TLCG_P2P_BACKEND` — sets status=`Rejected`, writes `metadata.rejectionNote`

**`BACKEND_URL = '/api/voucher'`** (Vercel proxy) — do NOT hardcode a direct GAS exec URL.

## Drive folder (`PURCHASE_REQUEST_FOLDER_ID`)

GAS reads folder ID via `getCfg_('PURCHASE_REQUEST_FOLDER_ID', '1SJ-pUa6jg2rmJTzle-TvvSNrKMUduvx3')` — same pattern as `DRIVE_VOUCHER_FOLDER_ID` in `TLCG_CASH_BACKEND.gs`.
Set Script Property after deploy: key=`PURCHASE_REQUEST_FOLDER_ID`, value=`1SJ-pUa6jg2rmJTzle-TvvSNrKMUduvx3`.

